{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place flour, baking powder and salt in mixing bowl then mix <b>5 sec\/speed 3<b>.","Add 75 g butter and mix <b>10 sec\/speed 4<b>.","Place a jug on mixing bowl lid and weigh in milk then remove. Without measuring cup, set <b>speed 3<b> and add milk gradually through hole in mixing bowl lid until mixture comes together (you may not need the full amount). Tip out onto a floured surface. Roll out to a rectangle approx. 1 cm thick.","Place remaining 25 g butter in mixing bowl and melt <b>2 min\/90°C\/speed 1<b>. Meanwhile, line 2 baking trays with baking paper. Brush dough with melted butter.","Lay bacon slices over dough, leaving a 2 cm border on one long edge.","Place garlic (if using), onions and parsley in mixing bowl then chop <b>5 sec\/speed 5<b>. Transfer to a bowl and set aside.","Place Cheddar in mixing bowl and grate <b>3 sec\/speed 8<b>.","Add cream cheese then transfer to bowl with onion mixture and mix with spatula to combine thoroughly. Spread evenly over bacon.","Brush the 2 cm border with water then, starting with the other long edge, roll up rectangle into a log, sealing the wet border to the roll. Transfer to a prepared tray and place in fridge for 20 minutes. Meanwhile, preheat oven to 180°C.","Slice chilled roll into 12 pieces (2-3 cm) and place flat on prepared trays. Bake for 15-20 minutes (180°C) until golden.","Serve warm."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["250 g plain flour, plus extra for dusting","3 tsp baking powder","½ tsp fine sea salt","100 g unsalted butter, cold, diced","250 g whole milk","8 slices back bacon","1 garlic clove              (optional)","80 g onions, quartered","10 g fresh parsley leaves","100 g Cheddar cheese, cut in pieces (2 cm)","100 g cream cheese","water, for brushing"]}],"id":"r284357","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-gFScAxRujkU\/XZaomOoYo0I\/AAAAAAAAhLo\/Vnx17OOBJlk2Tj5mkVDdlhuOe-6fVeiAgCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_sG8YlU0eoYjYXwq_.png","title":"Bacon Roly-polies","publishedAt":"2018-12-03T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"9.3 g","fat":"15.9 g","uom":"per 1 piece","carbohydrates":"17.5 g","calories":"1058 kJ \/ 254 kcal"},"usefulItems":"rolling pin, pastry brush, jug, baking trays, long sharp knife, baking paper, refrigerator, oven","hintsAndTricks":["Delicious savoury pastries made with the irresistible flavours of salty bacon and melted cheese. An easy and creative breakfast option that will be enjoyed by kids and adults alike."],"basicInfo":["easy","25m","1h","12 pieces"]}